description:
Lucky you!!

In order to spread the good news, Matt & Bowen are sharing their latest Patreon Episode with ALL of Culturistas Nation! Currently, they are in the midst of recapping Season 10 of Drag Race -- and you can follow along if you subscribe to the Las Culturistas Patreon page. Today, they break down Episode 3!

For only $5 a month (that's LESS than HULU!!), you get MORE Las Culturistas content weekly (that's EVERY week!!). SUBSCRIBE NOW!!
